      "startTime": 5.8182311687
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-buriburi001.m4a",
      "text": "久しブリブリブリッ！？\nじゃなくて！　どうして、戻ってきたんだブリ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5666666667,
      "endTime": 16.0601252239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま、ブリスケ。あなたを一人には出来ない\n大好きなお魚達の平和を守るため、私も戦う……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2666666667,
      "endTime": 24.7201138179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-buriburi002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんがオラを……大……ス……キ……？\nもしかして風にヒラメくコイしいこの気持ちは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9333333333,
      "endTime": 38.5034997304,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_dream-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6666666999945
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-buriburi003.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん。この戦いが終わって、オラが一回り成長して\nブリになれた暁には……君に伝えたいことがあるブリ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7,
      "endTime": 49.6640625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "うん？　分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8666666667,
      "endTime": 52.621632735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえブリスケ！　なんでお魚さん達は争っているの？\n同じ魚同士、みんなで仲良く出来ないのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8333333333,
      "endTime": 62.017958768199996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-buriburi004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……オラ達『おさかな☆HEAVEN』は\n「人間に食べられたい」魚達の集まりブリ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2333333333,
      "endTime": 69.833333524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-buriburi005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、反対勢力である『オサカナ♦HELL』の魚達は\n「人間に食べられたくない」ブリ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.0333333333,
      "endTime": 77.38908322649999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "このままだと人間界にも影響を及ぼしかねないわね\nなんとしてでも『オサカナ♦HELL』を鎮圧しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6,
      "endTime": 86.89999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-buriburi006.m4a",
      "text": "『オサカナ♦HELL』も元は「人間に食べられたい」\nと同じ志を掲げていた。だから話せばきっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1,
      "endTime": 96.3360837936,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15966.666666700006
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17600.000000000007
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 19400.000000000007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "maguro",
      "speakerName": "マグ田マグロウ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-maguro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-maguro001.m4a",
      "text": "フッ、いつまでそんな生ぬるいことを言ってるマグ？\n鮮度の落ちた貴様らは我々が殲滅する。とりゃー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5333333333,
      "endTime": 107.5704758962,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "大変っ！　マグロの大群に囲まれた！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7666666667,
      "endTime": 111.63628107710001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-buriburi007.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……お前はオラの幼馴染……マグ田マグロウ！？\n『オサカナ♦HELL』の総長は君だったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8333333333,
      "endTime": 122.3022710164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ブリスケに酷いことをしないでっ！\nなんで……なんでマグロウ達は人間を恨むの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5,
      "endTime": 129.3362811088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "maguro",
      "speakerName": "マグ田マグロウ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-maguro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-maguro002.m4a",
      "text": "ふんっ。俺達魚よりも肉が好きな人間が悪いマグ！\n肉が好きなら一生食ってろ！　もう魚は食わせん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5333333333,
      "endTime": 139.8082087835,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 733.3333333999974
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7400.0000000000055
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "えーと……本当は食べてほしいけど、お魚よりも\nお肉の人気の方が高いから怒ってる、のかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140,
      "endTime": 151.15458087919998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fishheaven-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "fishheaven-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、嫉妬ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3666666667,
      "endTime": 152.9405441682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "maguro",
      "speakerName": "マグ田マグロウ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-maguro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03-maguro003.m4a",
      "text": "黙れいっ！　小娘！　べ、別に食べてほしくなんか……\nに、に、肉なんかにも嫉妬するわけないマグ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1333333333,
      "endTime": 166.1978005727,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
